Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.48,0:02:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  您乐意坐坐的话  我确信...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Grace, if you'd like to sit, I'm sure that--
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.19,0:02:53.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们从中午就在等\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We've been here since midday.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.12,0:03:05.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我经常发现东方人的时间观念与我们不同\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Easterners have a difference sense of time, I've often found.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.61,0:03:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有次我在布拉佛斯等萨拉多·桑恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once I was waiting for Salladhor Saan here in Braavos.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.52,0:03:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要一起运送三船上好的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Together, we were going to run three shiploads of the finest...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.03,0:03:44.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎来到铁金库\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Welcome to the Iron Bank.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.48,0:03:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请坐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please, sit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.21,0:04:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什么可以效劳的  史坦尼斯大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What can we do for you, Lord Stannis?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.51,0:04:14.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们面前的是拜拉席恩家族的史坦尼斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Stannis of the House Baratheon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.98,0:04:16.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安达尔人和先民的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}King of the Andals and the First Men,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.70,0:04:19.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七国的统治者暨全境守护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lord of the Seven Kingdoms and Protector of the Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.54,0:04:25.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现今占据铁王座的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Iron Throne is currently occupied
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.47,0:04:27.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是拜拉席恩家族的托曼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}by Tommen of the House Baratheon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.42,0:04:29.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安达尔人和先民的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}King of the Andals and the First Men,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七国的统治者暨全境守护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lord of the Seven Kingdoms and Protector of the Realm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.03,0:04:34.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不是我的血亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He shares no blood with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.39,0:04:38.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是乱伦所生的孽种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is a bastard born of incest.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.36,0:04:40.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他死去的哥哥一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As was his brother before him.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.15,0:04:43.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  我们听过这个故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, we have heard this story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:45.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是故事  这是事实\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's not a story. It's the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.09,0:04:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,国王的外祖父有不同的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The king's grandfather tells a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.64,0:04:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讲的是嫉妒心作祟的叔父\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A story about a jealous uncle
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.28,0:04:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,企图篡夺合法国王的王座\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}whose attempts to usurp the throne from the rightful king
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.01,0:04:58.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使得七大王国付出了无数鲜血和金子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}cost the Seven Kingdoms dearly in blood and gold.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.78,0:05:00.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你借给他的金子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Gold you loaned him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.38,0:05:04.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而你认为血统给了你向我们讨金子的资格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you feel your blood gives you a claim on our gold?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.34,0:05:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世上没人比我更有资格\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}More than any man living.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.37,0:05:10.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狭海对岸  你们的书中充斥着\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Across the Narrow Sea, your books are filled
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.11,0:05:13.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"篡夺者"  "疯子"  "血统继承"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with words like "usurper" and "madman"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.51,0:05:15.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些字眼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and "blood right."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.45,0:05:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这里  我们的书里满是数字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Here, our books are filled with numbers.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.31,0:05:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们更喜欢数字讲述的故事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We prefer the stories they tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.81,0:05:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更直白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}More plain.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.75,0:05:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,更难曲解\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Less open to interpretation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.28,0:05:32.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你麾下还有多少兵士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How many fighting men remain loyal to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.35,0:05:33.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四千\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}4,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.65,0:05:35.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有多少艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And how many ships do you have?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.45,0:05:37.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还浮在水上的  戴佛斯爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The ones still afloat, Ser Davos,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.69,0:05:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是沉在黑水湾底的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}not at the bottom of Blackwater Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.28,0:05:43.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三十二艘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}32.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.34,0:05:45.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们龙石岛上出产多少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And how much wheat and barley and beef
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.43,0:05:47.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小麦  大麦  牛肉  猪肉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and pork do you produce on Dragonstone
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:52.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,养活这四千人和三十二艘船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to feed your 4,000 men on your 32 ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.90,0:05:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}None.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.85,0:05:59.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也看得出为何在我们看来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can see why these numbers seem unlikely to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.30,0:06:02.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些数字预示不出美好的结局\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to a happy ending from our perspective.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.99,0:06:08.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕我们只好婉拒你的请求\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm afraid we must respectfully decline your request.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是还要多谢你亲自光临\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But we thank you for paying us the honor of your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.80,0:06:22.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.64,0:06:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是大人  戴佛斯·席渥斯爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not a lord, Ser Davos Seaworth.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.84,0:06:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这儿也当不了爵爷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You would not be either here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.88,0:06:29.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在布拉佛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In Braavos,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.86,0:06:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是不会赏给窃贼封号的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}thieves are not rewarded with titles.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.71,0:06:34.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,严格来说  我没强取豪夺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, strictly speaking, I didn't do the thieving.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.45,0:06:36.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是海盗的作为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That would be the pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.08,0:06:39.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不过是将他们所获从一处运往另一处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I just moved what they stole from one place to another.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这就是史坦尼斯国王对我所犯之罪的惩罚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is the payment that was demanded by King Stannis for my crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.49,0:06:46.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我认为赏罚严明无欺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I consider it an honest accounting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个诚实的人  也是你们最好的机会\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's an honest man and he's your best chance
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,收回丢进维斯特洛无底洞的钱\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to get back the money you've sunk into Westeros.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.56,0:06:54.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想那是一大笔钱  战争是很昂贵的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Which is a lot, I imagine. Wars are expensive.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.65,0:06:55.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争已经结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The war is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.82,0:06:58.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要史坦尼斯还活着  战争就没有结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As long as Stannis lives, the war is not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.85,0:07:00.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁才是君临真正的掌权人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who's the real power in King's Landing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:02.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-戴佛斯爵士  -请回答\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Ser Davos... - Humor me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.34,0:07:06.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-泰温·兰尼斯特  -泰温·兰尼斯特多大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Tywin Lannister. - How old is Tywin Lannister?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.45,0:07:09.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-六十七  -六十七  他死后谁来掌权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- 67. - 67. And when he dies, who's in command?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.42,0:07:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个乱伦所生的半大男孩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A half-grown boy, the product of incest?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.54,0:07:16.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瑟曦·兰尼斯特  被臣民瞧不起的太后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cersei Lannister, a queen whose people despise her?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.98,0:07:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詹姆·兰尼斯特  最负盛名的事迹是杀害\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jaime Lannister, a man best known for killing the king
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.57,0:07:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他誓言保护的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he was sworn to protect?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.32,0:07:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰温死后  你们支持谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When Tywin's gone, who do you back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.27,0:07:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是以后的问题\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That is a problem for another time.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.24,0:07:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  我认为这问题迫在眉睫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Begging your pardon, I think it's a problem for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.58,0:07:34.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维斯特洛只剩一位可靠的领袖\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's only one reliable leader left in Westeros.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.13,0:07:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,史坦尼斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Stannis.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.70,0:07:38.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他有继承权\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's got the birthright.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.35,0:07:39.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正当盛年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's in his prime.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是久经考验的统帅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's a tried and tested battle commander.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.46,0:07:44.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且还债的时候绝不耍嘴皮子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he doesn't just talk about paying people back,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.64,0:07:45.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而是付诸行动\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he does it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.69,0:07:52.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭望哨看到一艘海盗船冲他们而来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The lookout sees a pirate ship sailing their way.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.97,0:07:54.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长喊大副\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The captain shouts to his first mate,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"拿我的红上衣来"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Bring me my red shirt."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.03,0:07:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大副拿来红上衣  船长穿在身上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The first mate brings the red shirt and the captain puts it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.89,0:08:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当海盗试图登船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when the pirates try to board,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.58,0:08:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勇敢的船长带领手下赢得了胜利\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the brave captain leads his men to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.43,0:08:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,几天之后  瞭望哨大叫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A few days later, the lookout screams,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.60,0:08:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"两艘海盗船"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Two pirate ships!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.68,0:08:13.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船员抖如筛糠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The crew is shivering like scared mice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.55,0:08:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是英勇无畏的船长高呼\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But the courageous captain hollers,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.52,0:08:17.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"拿我的红上衣来"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Bring me my red shirt!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.49,0:08:19.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战斗结束后  大副问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After the battle, the first mate asks,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"船长  为什么开战前你要穿红上衣"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Captain, why do you call for your red shirt before battle?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:24.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长答道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The captain replies,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.90,0:08:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"这样即使我受伤  你们也看不到我流血"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"So that if I am stabbed, you will not see me bleed."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.63,0:08:30.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二天一早  瞭望哨尖声叫嚷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The next morning the lookout screams,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.50,0:08:33.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"十艘海盗船\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"10 pirate ships!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.52,0:08:35.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被包围了"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We are surrounded!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船员们沉默了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The crew goes silent.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.13,0:08:40.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们看向勇敢的船长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They all look to their brave captain,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.86,0:08:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等待他惯常的号令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}waiting for his usual command.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.92,0:08:45.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,船长冷静如常  大喝一声\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Calm as ever, the captain bellows...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.14,0:08:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"拿我的屎黄色裤子来"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"Bring me my brown pants!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.29,0:08:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为她们见过不讲这段子的海盗吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You think they ever met a pirate who didn't tell them that joke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戴佛斯\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Davos.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你正在龙石岛的地牢里烂着呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I heard you were rotting in a dungeon in Dragonstone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.41,0:09:00.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只烂了一半\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only half rotted.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.77,0:09:06.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来加入我们  朋友  来吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Join us, my friend. Join us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.10,0:09:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这位是娜拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is Lhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.47,0:09:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这位是...  -我才是娜拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- And this is-- - I am Lhara.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.89,0:09:17.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她可是个艺术家  真的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She's an artist, this one, truly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.13,0:09:20.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思  没时间  我们黎明就起航\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No time, I'm afraid. We sail at sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.85,0:09:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我  我们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You, me-- we.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:29.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从前我以为这男人爱我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once I thought this man loved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在才知道他瞧不起我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now I know he despises me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.42,0:09:37.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他想看我穷困孤单地死在寒冷的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wants to see me die poor and alone on some cold--
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.66,0:09:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不会孤单\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You won't be alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.46,0:09:50.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不会受穷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you won't be poor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.56,0:10:01.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有一箱子好东西丢在你家里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a chest of the good stuff left back at your house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,交给你妻子了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I gave it to your wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.47,0:10:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真不够朋友  我的朋友\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're not my friend, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.85,0:10:12.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黎明再见\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll see you at sunrise.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.67,0:10:17.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我限你满月前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I give you until the full moon
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.58,0:10:21.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令所有铁渣离开北境\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to order all ironborn scum out of the North
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.17,0:10:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回到你们称其为家的屎群岛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and back to those shit-stained rocks you call home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.25,0:10:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,满月第一夜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}On the first night of the full moon,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.94,0:10:29.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会肃清所有仍在我们领土上的岛民\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I will hunt down every islander still on our lands
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.82,0:10:31.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并活剥其皮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and flay them living,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像我剥在临冬城发现的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the way I flayed the 20 ironborn scum
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.44,0:10:36.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那二十个铁渣一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I found at Winterfell.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.47,0:10:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盒中有份特别的礼物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In the box you'll find a special gift--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是席恩最爱的玩具\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Theon's favorite toy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.09,0:10:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我夺走时他哭了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He cried when I took it away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.57,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻离开北境  否则席恩将一份份\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Leave the North now or more boxes will follow
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.53,0:10:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随盒而至\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}with more Theon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.88,0:10:55.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,署名  拉姆斯·雪诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Signed Ramsay Snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.31,0:10:58.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恐怖堡公爵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}natural born son of Roose Bolton,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.63,0:11:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和北境守护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lord of the Dreadfort
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.51,0:11:02.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卢斯·波顿之子"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Warden of the North."
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.49,0:11:04.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.99,0:11:07.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们剥我们同胞的皮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They skinned our countrymen
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.64,0:11:10.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,残害我的弟弟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and they mutilated my brother,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.67,0:11:12.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的王子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}your prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.73,0:11:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们的王子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.10,0:11:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们对我弟弟如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everything they've done to him,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.56,0:11:19.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是对你们如何\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they've also done to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.61,0:11:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爽  爽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若是他们伤害我们的王子  却不用付出代价\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As long as they can hurt our prince with impunity,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.99,0:11:28.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,铁种两个字就白叫了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the word ironborn means nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.95,0:11:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去左边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Go left.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.86,0:12:05.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-席恩·葛雷乔伊  -我不知道...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Theon Greyjoy. - I don't know--
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.87,0:12:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我来找席恩·葛雷乔伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm here for Theon Greyjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.30,0:12:08.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带我去地牢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take me to the dungeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.99,0:12:10.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他不在地牢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's not in the dungeons.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.12,0:12:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-最右边的笼子  -谢谢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Last cage on the right. - Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.89,0:12:42.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这边\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.23,0:12:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们回家\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We're going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:00.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.68,0:13:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事了  是我  雅拉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's all right. It's me, Yara.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.51,0:13:08.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗不了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You can't trick me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.17,0:13:11.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他  告诉他你骗不了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell him. Tell him you couldn't trick me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.31,0:13:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没骗你  席恩  我来救你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm not tricking you, Theon. I'm saving you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.56,0:13:15.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是席恩  是臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not Theon! Reek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.12,0:13:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭佬  我的名字是臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Reek! My name is Reek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.63,0:13:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果被他们堵在这儿  我们就出不去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If they catch us in here, we're trapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:19.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拉他一把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Help me with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.11,0:13:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  不要\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, you can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.53,0:13:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-不要  -你是席恩·葛雷乔伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You can't! - You're Theon Greyjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.60,0:13:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我不相信她  我知道我是谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, I don't believe her! I know who I am!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.23,0:13:30.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是臭佬  臭佬  忠诚的臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Reek! Reek! Loyal Reek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.90,0:13:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听话的臭佬  我一直都是臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good Reek! I've always been Reek!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.34,0:13:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一个美好的夜晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This is turning into a lovely evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.01,0:14:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是臭佬  忠诚的臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm Reek! Loyal Reek!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Theon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.66,0:14:32.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我弟弟还给我  就饶了你其余的手下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Give me my brother and no more of your men will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.03,0:14:35.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的卵蛋可比他以前的大多了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You've got bigger balls than he ever did.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.10,0:14:41.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可你挂着这么大的卵蛋\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But with those big balls of yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能跑多快呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}how fast can you run?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.59,0:15:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,划到大船去  快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make for the ship, now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.18,0:15:03.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你弟弟还没来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But your brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.07,0:15:05.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我弟弟死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My brother is dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.80,0:15:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要让你享受一把\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have a treat for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.61,0:15:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作为奖励\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.11,0:15:20.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奖励\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Reward?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.10,0:15:23.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Reek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚闯进来的那些畜生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Those creatures who came in the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.35,0:15:28.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们想带走你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}they wanted to take you away.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.80,0:15:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你没让他们得逞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you didn't let them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.01,0:15:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你表现得很忠诚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You remained loyal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.89,0:15:37.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我...我不想被他们带走\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I-- I didn't want them to take me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.40,0:15:39.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我害怕极了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was so scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:42.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-我不想让他们...  -是的  臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- I didn't want them-- - Yes, yes, Reek.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.60,0:15:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泡个澡吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.81,0:15:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你准备的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.16,0:16:00.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把身上的破布脱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remove those rags.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.46,0:16:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有裤子  臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The britches, too, Reek.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.49,0:16:24.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把裤子脱了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Take them off.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.22,0:17:53.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你爱我吗  臭佬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you love me, Reek?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.83,0:18:01.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然爱  大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, of course, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.23,0:18:05.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:07.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我要你为我做件事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Because I need you to do something for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.75,0:18:10.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常重要的事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Something very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.13,0:18:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一座城堡  你知道的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There's a castle, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:16.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一帮坏人占领了那座城堡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some bad men hold this castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.41,0:18:20.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你帮我夺回这座城堡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need your help to take this castle back.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.44,0:18:25.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可我怎样...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But how can--
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.53,0:18:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要你演个角色\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I need you to play a role.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.01,0:18:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假扮成另一个人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To pretend to be someone you're not.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.33,0:18:39.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,假扮成谁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Pretend to be who?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.96,0:18:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,席恩·葛雷乔伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Theon Greyjoy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.43,0:19:56.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,225.6)}你面前的是坦格利安家族的"风暴降生"
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,240)}丹妮莉丝·坦格利安一世
