Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.08,0:20:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,240)}弥林女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.08,0:20:02.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,240)}安达尔人和先民的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.23,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,240)}草海上的卡丽熙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.72,0:20:08.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,240)}解放者  龙之母
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.63,0:20:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,240)}别害怕  我的朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.36,0:20:16.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,240)}女王请你上前说话
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.46,0:20:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是个牧羊人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He is a goatherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.28,0:20:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说他曾祈祷您能战胜奴隶主们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He says he prayed for your victory against the slave masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.10,0:20:37.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我感谢他的祈祷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thank him for his prayers.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.13,0:20:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说是您的龙所为\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was your dragons, he says.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.48,0:20:57.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们今早袭击了他的羊群\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They came this morning for his flock.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.92,0:21:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他希望自己没有冒犯女王陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He hopes he has not offended Your Grace,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.63,0:21:06.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但他现在一无所有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but now he has nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.21,0:21:09.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告诉他  对于他遭受的苦难  我很抱歉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tell this man I am sorry for his hardship.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:12.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没法让他的山羊起死回生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I cannot bring back his goats,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.28,0:21:18.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我会以三倍的价格赔偿他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I will see he is paid their value three times over.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.48,0:21:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召见下一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Send the next one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.98,0:21:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,225.6)}西茨达拉·佐·洛拉克大人向女王陛下请愿
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.53,0:21:57.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H86E8FC&\bord0\fs22\fsp1\b1\pos(193,225.6)}西茨达拉·佐·洛拉克大人可以自己张嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.72,0:22:11.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹妮莉丝女王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Queen Daenerys.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.95,0:22:14.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的美貌如传闻中一样夺目\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tales of your beauty were not exaggerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.16,0:22:16.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.24,0:22:19.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,洛拉克是弥林最古老和荣耀的家族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mine is one of the oldest and proudest families in Meereen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.81,0:22:22.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很荣幸接见你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Then it is my honor to receive you.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.23,0:22:25.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的父亲是弥林最受尊敬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My father, one of Meereen's most respected
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.12,0:22:27.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和爱戴的市民  他负责监督\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and beloved citizens, oversaw the restoration
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.90,0:22:30.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弥林伟大建筑的重建和维护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and maintenance of its greatest landmarks.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.45,0:22:31.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括这座金字塔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This pyramid included.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.33,0:22:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我可要感谢他的功劳\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}For that, he has my gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.01,0:22:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该见见他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I should be honored to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.90,0:22:37.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您见过了  陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.81,0:22:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您将他钉死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You crucified him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.80,0:22:43.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我祈祷您在有生之年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I pray you'll never live to see
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.36,0:22:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会看到亲人遭此毒手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}a member of your family treated so cruelly.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.62,0:22:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你父亲钉死了无辜的孩童\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your father crucified innocent children.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.90,0:22:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲反对钉死那些孩童\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My father spoke out against crucifying those children.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.79,0:22:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他谴责这一罪行  但是被驳回了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He decried it as a criminal act, but was overruled.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.04,0:22:59.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以罪行回应罪行  这算公道吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Is it justice to answer one crime with another?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.43,0:23:01.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对你失去父亲感到遗憾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am sorry you no longer have a father,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.48,0:23:04.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我对伟主们的处置不是罪行\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but my treatment of the masters was no crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.30,0:23:07.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要谨记这一点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'd be wise to remember that.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.98,0:23:10.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,木已成舟\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What's done is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.17,0:23:14.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是女王  而我是弥林的仆人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are the queen and I am a servant of Meereen.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.08,0:23:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不希望这里的传统被连根拔去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A servant who does not wish to see its traditions eradicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.28,0:23:20.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你所说的传统是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what traditions do you speak of?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.67,0:23:22.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,葬礼仪式\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The tradition of funeral rite.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.75,0:23:25.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体面地安葬在圣恩神庙中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Proper burial in the Temple of the Graces.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.18,0:23:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父亲和一百六十二名弥林贵族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My father and 162 noble Meereenese
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.53,0:23:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仍然被钉在柱子上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}are still nailed to those posts,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.65,0:23:34.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受秃鹫啄食  在阳光下腐烂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}carrion for vultures, rotting in the sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.25,0:23:47.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  我请求您命令放下这些人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Grace, I ask that you order these men taken down
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.07,0:23:49.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他们能够被体面地安葬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so that they might receive proper burials.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.44,0:23:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些被高贵的弥林人钉死的奴隶孩童怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And what of the slave children these noble Meereenese crucified?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.82,0:23:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们也在阳光下腐烂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They were rotting in the sun as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.28,0:23:59.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你会请求我体面地安葬他们吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Would you have begged me for their right to a proper burial?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.55,0:24:02.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,陛下  我不能为伟主们的行为辩护\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your Grace, I cannot defend the actions of the masters.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.62,0:24:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只能以一个敬爱父亲的儿子的身份请求您\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I can only speak to you as a son who loved his father.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.58,0:24:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我取下他的尸首\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me take his body down.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.80,0:24:11.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我将他带到神庙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me have him brought to the temple
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.33,0:24:12.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,体面地安葬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and buried with dignity
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.92,0:24:15.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让他在阴间求得安宁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so that he might find peace in the next world.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.13,0:24:22.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安葬你的父亲吧  西茨达拉·佐·洛拉克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Bury your father, Hizdahr zo Loraq.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.64,0:24:29.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢您  我的女王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, my queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有多少人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How many more?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.97,0:24:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有二百一十二个请愿者等待觐见  陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}There are 212 supplicants waiting, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.21,0:24:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二百一十二个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}212?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.48,0:24:58.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,召见下一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Send the next one in.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.55,0:25:03.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会议不是每回都这么早开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}These meetings aren't always going to be this early, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.01,0:25:05.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我昨天睡得晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was up late last night.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:06.43,0:25:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说起来  我是不是算个什么大臣了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So, does this mean I am a master of something now?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.50,0:25:12.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,财政  海政\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Coins, ships?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.32,0:25:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰温大人和我早已决定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lord Tywin and I already determined
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.76,0:25:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我担任海政大臣  那时你还没...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that I shall be the Master of Ships long before you--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:23.24,0:25:24.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泰温大人  能出席御前会议\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lord Tywin, it's a great honor
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.80,0:25:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在下倍感荣幸  我...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to have been granted a seat on this council. I--
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.22,0:25:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,审判今天下午开始\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The trial begins this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.37,0:25:31.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们只有一上午的时间处理国事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We only have the morning for affairs of state.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.59,0:25:32.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shall we begin?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.32,0:25:37.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人在河间地见到桑铎·克里冈  大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sandor Clegane has been spotted in the Riverlands, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:37.66,0:25:39.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,懦夫和叛徒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A coward and a traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.25,0:25:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小小鸟儿说猎狗杀了我们五个士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My birds tell me the Hound slaughtered five of our soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.43,0:25:46.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我相信他还说了"去他妈的国王"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I believe the phrase "fuck the king" was uttered.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:46.41,0:25:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可耻\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Disgraceful.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.95,0:25:49.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给多少钱能让普通士兵\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What would it take to make the common soldier
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.81,0:25:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脑袋发热  愿与猎狗搏命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}stupid enough to try his luck with the Hound?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.24,0:25:55.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十枚银鹿足矣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}10 silver stags seems a generous bounty.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.25,0:25:57.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加到一百枚  还有何事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Make it 100. What else?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:58.14,0:26:00.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东方又传来了消息  大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}More whispers from the east, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.48,0:26:02.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个坦格利安家的女孩吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The Targaryen girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.23,0:26:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丹妮莉丝已在弥林安定下来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Daenerys has taken up residence in Meereen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.05,0:26:08.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她征服了那座城市  成了那里的女王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She has conquered the city and rules as its queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.60,0:26:09.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿什么征服的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Conquered with what?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.82,0:26:12.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她带领着一支无垢者大军  太后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She commands an army of Unsullied, my queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.05,0:26:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,约有八千人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Some 8,000 strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.31,0:26:17.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有佣兵次子团相助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She has a company of sellswords-- the Second Sons.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.89,0:26:20.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她有两位骑士进言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She has two knights advising her--
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.35,0:26:23.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乔拉·莫尔蒙和巴利斯坦·赛尔弥\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Jorah Mormont and Barristan Selmy.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.77,0:26:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且她还有三条龙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And she has three dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:25.84,0:26:27.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三条幼龙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Baby dragons.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:27.15,0:26:29.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它们一年比一年大  陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Larger every year, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.54,0:26:32.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫尔蒙是我们派去监视她的探子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mormont is spying on her for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.64,0:26:35.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不再是了  他现在似乎完全效忠于她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No longer. He appears to be fully devoted to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.88,0:26:38.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至于巴利斯坦爵士  看起来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As for Ser Barristan, it would seem
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.93,0:26:43.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们低估了他对被剥夺御林铁卫身份的不满\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he took his dismissal from the Kingsguard a bit harder than anticipated.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.35,0:26:44.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他老了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He's an old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.01,0:26:47.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没法保护我儿子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wasn't fit to protect my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.24,0:26:49.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在他护卫时  乔佛里没有死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Joffrey didn't die on his watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.85,0:26:52.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将他免职是为羞辱  而且愚蠢至极\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dismissing him was as insulting as it was stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:52.79,0:26:55.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别告诉我您还担心世界另一头的孩子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Don't tell me you're worried about a child halfway across the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:55.85,0:26:59.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个孩子的身边有两位老将辅佐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A child with two seasoned warriors counseling her
Dialogue: 0,0:26:59.54,0:27:02.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身后有一支强大的军队  太后陛下\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and a powerful army at her back, Your Grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:02.54,0:27:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦里斯大人说得对\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lord Varys is right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.34,0:27:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在厄索斯亲眼见过无垢者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have been to Essos and seen the Unsullied firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.64,0:27:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们打起仗来很有一套\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}They are very impressive on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.87,0:27:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但床上功夫逊色不少\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Less so in the bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.53,0:27:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三百年来  依靠龙没打胜过一场仗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dragons haven't won a war in 300 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.19,0:27:17.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赢得战争的从来都是军队\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Armies win them all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.68,0:27:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须解决掉她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She must be dealt with.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.74,0:27:22.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么解决  大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How, my lord?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.34,0:27:23.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用武力吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By force?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.74,0:27:25.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逼不得已当然要这么做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Eventually, if it comes to that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:27.77,0:27:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那些小小鸟去得了弥林吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Can your little birds find their way into Meereen?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.20,0:27:33.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应是没有问题  首相大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Most certainly, my Lord Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.10,0:27:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提利尔大人  劳烦你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Mmm. Lord Tyrell, be a good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.66,0:27:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拿我的纸笔来\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fetch my quill and paper.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.89,0:28:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥柏伦亲王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Prince Oberyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.57,0:28:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦里斯大人...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lord Varys...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.38,0:28:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦里斯就行了  我并非贵族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Only Varys. I'm not actually a nobleman.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.33,0:28:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必称我为"大人"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No one is under obligation to call me lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.96,0:28:10.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但大家都这么称呼你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And yet everyone does.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:13.21,0:28:15.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎很了解无垢者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You seem quite knowledgeable about the Unsullied.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.72,0:28:17.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在厄索斯待过很长时间吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you spend much time in Essos?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.91,0:28:19.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五年\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Five years.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:20.58,0:28:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能告诉我原因吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}May I ask why?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.77,0:28:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个世界如此辽阔美丽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}'Tis a big and beautiful world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:25.61,0:28:27.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而大多数人从生到死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Most of us live and die
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.49,0:28:29.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都在同一个角落里不挪窝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the same corner where we were born
Dialogue: 0,0:28:29.20,0:28:31.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没见识过别处的风景\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and never get to see any of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.90,0:28:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不想成为那种人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I don't want to be most of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.90,0:28:36.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁叫我们大多数人不是亲王呢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Most of us aren't princes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.18,0:28:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是厄索斯人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are from Essos.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.97,0:28:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具体是哪里  里斯吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Where? Lys?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.07,0:28:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听得出口音\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have an ear for accents.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.62,0:28:49.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早就没有口音了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've lost my accent entirely.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.55,0:28:51.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这我也听出来了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I have an ear for that as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.03,0:28:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是怎么来这儿的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:55.11,0:28:56.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说来话长\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It's a long story.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.96,0:28:58.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是不想告诉别人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One you don't like telling people.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:00.58,0:29:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只说给我信任的人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}People I trust.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.33,0:29:05.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的情妇艾拉莉亚一定会觉得你很有意思\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My paramour Ellaria, she would find you very interesting.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.45,0:29:07.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你应该去妓院见见她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You should come to the brothel and meet her.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:07.64,0:29:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们自备了美酒  可不像他们这儿的泔水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We brought our own wine, not the swill they serve here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.12,0:29:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有些可爱的小伙子陪着  不过...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We have some lovely boys on retainer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.11,0:29:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以前喜欢小伙子吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You did like boys before?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.65,0:29:22.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.20,0:29:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是喜欢姑娘了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Girls? Hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.35,0:29:26.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你别见怪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I hope you won't be offended
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.31,0:29:28.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,万万没想到你竟然喜欢姑娘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}when I say I never would have guessed.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.01,0:29:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没关系\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:29.48,0:29:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我对姑娘也不感兴趣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But I was never interested in girls, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.46,0:29:34.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-那你喜欢什么  -什么都不喜欢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- What then? - Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.95,0:29:37.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个人都有喜好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Everybody is interested in something.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.52,0:29:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not me.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.02,0:29:41.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当我看到欲望对人的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When I see what desire does to people,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:41.17,0:29:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对这个国家的影响\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}what it's done to this country,
Dialogue: 0,0:29:43.53,0:29:46.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很高兴没有参与其中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am very glad to have no part in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:47.51,0:29:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此外  人若不为欲念驱使\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Besides, the absence of desire
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.79,0:29:53.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,便能放开手脚追求别的东西\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}leaves one free to pursue other things.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.94,0:29:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Such as?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.03,0:30:34.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我猜猜  我被赦免了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Let me guess, I've been pardoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.42,0:30:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真要这样吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.56,0:30:55.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是父亲的命令\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Father's orders.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.07,0:30:58.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  我们绝不能让父亲失望\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Well, we mustn't disappoint Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.02,0:31:10.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弑君者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Kingslayer!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:57.25,0:32:01.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我  拜拉席恩家族的托曼一世\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I, Tommen of the House Baratheon, first of my Name,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.05,0:32:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安达尔人和先民的国王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}King of the Andals and the First Men,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:04.76,0:32:06.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七国的统治者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Lord of the Seven Kingdoms,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:06.96,0:32:10.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此宣布  我本人不参与庭审\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}do hereby recuse myself from this trial.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.22,0:32:13.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由全境守护者  御前首相\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tywin of the House Lannister, Hand of the King,
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.89,0:32:17.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰尼斯特家族的泰温  替我主持审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Protector of the Realm, will sit as judge in my stead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.76,0:32:21.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,协助他审判的还有马泰尔家族的奥柏伦亲王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And with him Prince Oberyn of the House Martell
Dialogue: 0,0:32:22.26,0:32:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及提利尔家族的梅斯大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and Lord Mace of the House Tyrell.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:25.97,0:32:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若被告确实有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And if found guilty...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.60,0:32:31.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愿诸神严惩不贷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}may the gods punish the accused.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.45,0:33:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兰尼斯特家族的提利昂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tyrion of the House Lannister,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:10.13,0:33:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,摄政太后指控你犯有弑君大罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you stand accused by the Queen Regent of regicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.08,0:33:17.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你杀害了乔佛里国王吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did you kill King Joffrey?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.97,0:33:19.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:20.12,0:33:22.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是你的妻子  珊莎夫人干的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did your wife, the Lady Sansa?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.89,0:33:24.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,据我所知不是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not that I know of.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:25.28,0:33:27.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那你说  他是怎么死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How would you say he died, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.08,0:33:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是被鸽子馅饼噎死的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Choked on his pigeon pie.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.65,0:33:33.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依你之见  罪在厨师\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So you would blame the bakers?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.67,0:33:36.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不然就是鸽子  反正怪不到我头上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Or the pigeons. Just leave me out of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:39.18,0:33:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传召第一位证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The crown may call its first witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:42.32,0:33:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们刚护着乔佛里国王从暴民中撤出\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once we'd got King Joffrey safely away from the mob,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.84,0:33:46.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小恶魔就突然发飙了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the Imp rounded on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.47,0:33:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他狠狠地给了国王一记耳光\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He slapped the king across the face
Dialogue: 0,0:33:48.66,0:33:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还骂陛下是残暴的蠢王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and called him a vicious idiot and a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:52.74,0:33:55.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是小恶魔第一次威胁乔佛里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It wasn't the first time the Imp threatened Joffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.06,0:33:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在这间王座厅里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Right here in this throne room,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.83,0:34:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他曾冲上台阶  大骂国王是蠢鹅\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he marched up those steps and called our king a halfwit.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.29,0:34:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还将先王陛下与疯王相提并论\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Compared his Grace to the Mad King
Dialogue: 0,0:34:01.95,0:34:04.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,言下之意  先王陛下必不得好死\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and suggested he'd meet the same fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:04.00,0:34:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,见我替国王争辩\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And when I spoke in the king's defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.19,0:34:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他竟威胁要杀了我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he threatened to have me killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.83,0:34:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么不告诉大家乔佛里当时在做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, why don't you tell them what Joffrey was doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:10.60,0:34:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-肃静  -他拿上膛的弩对着珊莎·史塔克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- Silence. - Pointing a loaded crossbow at Sansa Stark
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.78,0:34:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你则撕扯她的衣服  还殴打她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}while you tore at her clothes and beat her.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.70,0:34:16.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:18.22,0:34:21.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没问到你  不准答话\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You will not speak unless called upon.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:22.94,0:34:24.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你下去吧  马林爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're dismissed, Ser Meryn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:31.82,0:34:33.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石蜥毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Basilisk venom,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.39,0:34:36.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寡妇之血\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}widow's blood,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.90,0:34:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,附子草\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}wolfsbane,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.73,0:34:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夜影之水\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}essence of nightshade,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.55,0:34:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甜睡花\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}sweetsleep,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.85,0:34:45.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里斯之泪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}tears of Lys,
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.25,0:34:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼舞草\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}demon's dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:50.87,0:34:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞎眼毒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}blindeye--
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.88,0:34:54.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的意思很明白了  大学士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I think you have made your point, Grand Maester.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.27,0:34:56.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你库中有不少毒药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have a lot of poison in your store.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.19,0:34:58.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早没了  奥柏伦亲王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Had, Prince Oberyn.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.13,0:35:01.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的库藏被劫掠一空\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}My stores were plundered.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.21,0:35:02.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁抢走的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.75,0:35:05.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告提利昂·兰尼斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}By the accused, Tyrion Lannister,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:05.23,0:35:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这之前他以莫须有的罪名将我囚禁\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}after he had me wrongfully imprisoned.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:08.02,0:35:09.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大学士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Grand Maester,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.41,0:35:13.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你检验过乔佛里国王的遗体\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}you examined King Joffrey's corpse.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.11,0:35:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是否确实被人毒杀\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Was it without question poison that killed him?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.93,0:35:20.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫无疑问\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Without question.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.75,0:35:24.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是在国王的弄臣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This was found on the body of
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.76,0:35:27.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唐托斯·霍拉德的尸体上找到的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Dontos Hollard, the king's fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:27.67,0:35:31.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他最后一次露面时  将被告的妻子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He was last seen spiriting Sansa Stark,
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.82,0:35:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,珊莎·史塔克偷偷带离了婚宴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the wife of the accused, away from the feast.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.97,0:35:39.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,婚礼当天\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She wore this necklace
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.35,0:35:40.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她戴的正是这条项链\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the day of the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.92,0:35:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,里面发现了一种\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Residue of a most rare
Dialogue: 0,0:35:44.51,0:35:48.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最稀有最可怕的毒药的残渣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and terrible poison was found inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.71,0:35:52.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是从你那里偷走的毒药吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Was this one of the poisons stolen from your store?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.63,0:35:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  扼死者\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It was. The Strangler.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.50,0:35:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,七国内只有少数人拥有这种毒药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A poison few in the Seven Kingdoms possess.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.58,0:36:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被告正是用它杀死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And used to strike down the most noble child
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.97,0:36:07.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,受诸神眷顾而降生的天命之子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}the gods ever put on this good earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:14.88,0:36:16.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"今日之辱  我一定会报\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I will hurt you for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.75,0:36:19.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总有一天  当你自以为平安快活时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}A day will come when you think you are safe and happy
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.83,0:36:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜悦必将在你嘴里化成灰烬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and your joy will turn to ashes in your mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:36:22.56,0:36:24.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时你便知道  债已偿清"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and you will know the debt is paid."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.80,0:36:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你亲弟弟这么对你说的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your own brother said this to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:29.78,0:36:32.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在黑水湾大战之前不久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shortly before the Battle of Blackwater Bay.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:32.68,0:36:34.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我质疑他将乔佛里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I confronted him about his plans
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.72,0:36:36.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,推上前线的计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to put Joffrey on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.39,0:36:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,后来  攻城开始后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As it turned out, when the attack came,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.89,0:36:43.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小乔坚持留在城墙上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Joff insisted on remaining at the battlements.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.41,0:36:47.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他认为国王在场能鼓舞士气\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He believed his presence would inspire the troops.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.93,0:36:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提利昂说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tyrion said,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:50.78,0:36:53.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"到时你便知道  债已偿清"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"And you will know the debt is paid."
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.12,0:36:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么债\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What debt?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.47,0:36:58.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发现他在首相塔里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I discovered he'd been keeping whores
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.10,0:36:59.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓄养娼妓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}in the Tower of the Hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.87,0:37:02.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要他去妓院狎妓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I asked him to confine his salacious acts
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.72,0:37:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以免有失体面\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to the brothel where such behavior belongs.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.83,0:37:07.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他很不高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He wasn't pleased.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.13,0:37:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太后陛下  感谢您站出来当庭作证\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Thank you, Your Grace, for the courage of your testimony.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.24,0:37:32.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还记得他具体是怎么威胁的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you remember the precise nature of this threat?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.44,0:37:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得  大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm afraid I do, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.52,0:37:38.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他说  "那你或许该对我客气点\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He said, "Perhaps you should speak more softly to me, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.05,0:37:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪物很危险\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Monsters are dangerous
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.86,0:37:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而现在国王正如蚊蝇般死去"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and just now kings are dying like flies."
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.75,0:37:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是他在御前会议上说的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And he said this to you at a meeting of the small council?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.77,0:37:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:48.19,0:37:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在收到罗柏·史塔克的死讯之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After we received word of Robb Stark's death.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.22,0:37:53.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他听到这消息似乎并不高兴\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He didn't seem gladdened by the news.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.73,0:37:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也许与珊莎·史塔克成婚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Perhaps his marriage to Sansa Stark
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.99,0:37:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令他对北方佬抱有同情之心\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}had made him more sympathetic to the northern cause.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.77,0:38:04.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下去吧  瓦里斯大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You're excused, Lord Varys.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.51,0:38:09.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲  我能问证人一个问题吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Father, may I ask the witness one question?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.36,0:38:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就一个\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}One.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.29,0:38:22.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾说过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You once said
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.96,0:38:26.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果没有我  都城必会沦陷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that without me, this city would have faced certain defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.60,0:38:30.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说史书不会记载我的姓名\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You said the histories would never mention me,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.85,0:38:32.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你却不会忘记\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but you would not forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:34.59,0:38:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你忘了吗  瓦里斯大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you forgotten, Lord Varys?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:39.83,0:38:41.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遗憾的是  大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Sadly, my lord,
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.21,0:38:44.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我从不遗忘\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I never forget a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.47,0:38:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暂时休庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}We will adjourn for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.96,0:39:00.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一小时后鸣钟开庭\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Toll the bells in an hour's time.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.28,0:39:01.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退席\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Clear the court!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.89,0:39:24.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您要判您的亲生儿子死刑吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'd condemn your own son to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.77,0:39:27.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我谁也没判  审判尚未结束\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've condemned no one. The trial is not over.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.28,0:39:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是审判  是场闹剧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This isn't a trial. It's a farce.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:28.84,0:39:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道这全都是瑟曦操纵的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Cersei has manipulated everything and you know it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.06,0:39:32.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知还有这等事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know nothing of the sort.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:32.45,0:39:34.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-您向来厌恶提利昂  -他杀了国王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You've always hated Tyrion. - He killed his king.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.86,0:39:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也一样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}As did I.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.19,0:39:39.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您知道疯王对我下的最后一道命令是什么吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know the last order the Mad King gave me?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.66,0:39:41.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把您的首级呈给他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}To bring him your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:42.65,0:39:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救了您的命  好让您谋杀我弟弟吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saved your life so you could murder my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.00,0:39:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-这不是谋杀  是主持公道  -公道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- It won't be murder. It'll be justice. - Justice?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.94,0:39:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在履行身为御前首相的责任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm performing my sworn duty as Hand of the King.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:50.95,0:39:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果提利昂有罪  便应将他依罪惩处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}If Tyrion is found guilty, he will be punished accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.68,0:39:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-他会被处决  -不  是依罪惩处\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- He'll be executed. - No, he'll be punished accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:59.26,0:40:03.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您曾说过  家族就是传承  永远延续\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Once you said family is what lives on. All that lives on.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:04.24,0:40:07.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您说过要建立一个传承千年不朽的王朝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You told me about a dynasty that would last 1,000 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.83,0:40:10.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提利昂一死  您的王朝怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happens to your dynasty when Tyrion dies?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.09,0:40:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是御林铁卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm a Kingsguard,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:13.51,0:40:15.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发誓不娶妻生子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}forbidden by oath to carry on the family line.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.59,0:40:17.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很清楚你的誓言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm well aware of your oath.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.02,0:40:18.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的姓氏怎么办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happens to your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.75,0:40:22.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将来在战场上  谁来打起狮子旗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Who carries the lion banner into future battles?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:23.09,0:40:23.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您的侄子吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Your nephews?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.89,0:40:26.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蓝赛尔·兰尼斯特吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Lancel Lannister?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:26.83,0:40:28.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是那些个我连名字都记不清的家伙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Others whose names I don't even remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.63,0:40:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,若我宽恕杀害我外孙的凶手\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What happens to my dynasty
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.05,0:40:32.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的王朝又会怎样\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if I spare the life of my grandson's killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.78,0:40:34.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会由我延续下去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}It survives through me.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.92,0:40:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我将卸任御林铁卫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll leave the Kingsguard.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.30,0:40:43.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要您放提利昂一条生路\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'll take my place as your son and heir
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.30,0:40:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就继承您的家业\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}if you let Tyrion live.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.37,0:40:46.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成交\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Done.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:48.86,0:40:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等取证结束  宣判有罪后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When the testimony's concluded and a guilty verdict rendered,
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.71,0:40:53.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提利昂将有机会为自己进言\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tyrion will be given the chance to speak.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.72,0:40:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他请求宽恕  我便准许他加入守夜人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He'll plead for mercy. I'll allow him to join the Night's Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.84,0:41:02.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三天后  他将启程前往黑城堡\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}In three days' time, he'll depart for Castle Black
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.08,0:41:03.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在长城度过余生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and live out his days at the Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:03.92,0:41:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你则即刻脱下白袍\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You'll remove your white cloak immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.99,0:41:08.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,离开君临\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You will leave King's Landing
Dialogue: 0,0:41:08.43,0:41:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继承凯岩城公爵之位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to assume your rightful place at Casterly Rock.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.72,0:41:13.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,娶个门当户对的女人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You will marry a suitable woman
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.79,0:41:16.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为兰尼斯特家传宗接代\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and father children named Lannister.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:16.74,0:41:19.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,永远不准再背弃家族\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you'll never turn your back on your family again.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.85,0:41:26.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You have my word.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.15,0:41:28.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一言为定\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And you have mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.56,0:41:55.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不太顺利是吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Not going well, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:55.15,0:41:57.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你将被判有罪  -你也这么觉得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}- You're going to be found guilty. - Oh, you think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.40,0:42:00.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宣判后  你要正式请求宽恕\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}When you are, you need to enter a formal plea for mercy
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.26,0:42:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请求发配去长城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and ask to be sent to the Wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:02.94,0:42:04.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲会准的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Father's agreed to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.92,0:42:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他会网开一面  准你穿上黑衣\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He'll spare your life and allow you to join the Night's Watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.32,0:42:10.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奈德·史塔克不也得到了同样的承诺\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ned Stark was promised the same thing
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.24,0:42:11.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们都清楚他的下场\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and we both know how that turned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.80,0:42:14.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲不是乔佛里  他会守信\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Father is not Joffrey. He'll keep his word.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:14.07,0:42:15.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.97,0:42:20.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信我吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you trust me?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:25.01,0:42:26.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘴巴闭紧  不要口无遮拦\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Keep your mouth shut. No more outbursts.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:27.77,0:42:28.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就会结束的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This will all be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.72,0:42:47.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,传召下一位证人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}The crown may call its next witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.11,0:43:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,报上名字\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}State your name.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.09,0:43:26.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shae.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.41,0:43:28.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你愿意对诸神发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you swear by all the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:43:28.69,0:43:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所说的证词全都真实可靠吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}that your testimony will be true and honest?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.94,0:43:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我发誓\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I swear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.64,0:43:35.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你认识这个人吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you know this man?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.34,0:43:46.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  提利昂·兰尼斯特\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes. Tyrion Lannister.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:47.55,0:43:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么认识他的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How do you know him?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.01,0:43:51.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是他妻子珊莎夫人的侍女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was handmaiden to his wife Lady Sansa.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:52.63,0:43:55.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此人被指控谋杀乔佛里国王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}This man stands accused of murdering King Joffrey.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.06,0:43:58.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道些什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}What do you know of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:00.61,0:44:02.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道他有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I know that he's guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.01,0:44:05.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和珊莎一起密谋弑君\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He and Sansa planned it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:07.02,0:44:07.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:10.78,0:44:11.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,继续说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Continue.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.59,0:44:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她想为父亲  母亲和哥哥报仇\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She wanted revenge for her father, her mother, her brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:16.64,0:44:18.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她把他们的死都怪到国王头上\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}She blamed their deaths on the king.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.62,0:44:21.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提利昂乐意帮忙\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tyrion was happy to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.44,0:44:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他恨乔佛里  恨太后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He hated Joffrey. He hated the queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:26.24,0:44:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也恨您  大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He hated you, my lord.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.45,0:44:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他从大学士的房间偷来毒药\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He stole poison from the Grand Maester's chamber
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.76,0:44:33.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放进乔佛里的酒中\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}to put in Joffrey's wine.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.95,0:44:35.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你如何知道这么多\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How could you possibly know all this?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.43,0:44:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他为什么要向妻子的侍女泄露计划\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Why would he reveal such plans to his wife's maid?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.04,0:44:43.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不仅是她的侍女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wasn't just her maid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.47,0:44:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还是他的妓女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was his whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.84,0:44:50.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I beg your pardon?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:51.33,0:44:52.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说你是他的...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You said you were his...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:53.95,0:44:54.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妓女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}His whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.04,0:45:00.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他是怎么找上你的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}How did you come to be in his service?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.45,0:45:01.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是他抢走的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He stole me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:02.00,0:45:04.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我当时跟着别人  大人麾下的一名骑士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was with another man, a knight in your lordship's army.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.21,0:45:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提利昂来到军营后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But when Tyrion arrived at the camp,
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.51,0:45:09.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,派一个歹人进了我们帐篷\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}he sent one of his cutthroats into our tent.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.91,0:45:12.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打折了骑士的胳膊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He broke the knight's arm
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.30,0:45:13.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把我带去给了提利昂大人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and brought me to Lord Tyrion.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:14.61,0:45:16.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"你现在是我的了"  他说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"You belong to me now," He said.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:17.39,0:45:18.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我要你拿出浑身解数\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I want you to fuck me
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.54,0:45:20.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就当今晚是我人生最后一晚"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}like it's my last night in this world."
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.10,0:45:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肃静  肃静\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Silence. Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.86,0:45:28.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.28,0:45:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我做了什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Did I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:31.95,0:45:34.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你拿出了浑身解数  就当是他人生最后一晚\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Fuck him like it was his last night in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:36.82,0:45:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他所有的要求我都照办\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did everything he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.22,0:45:41.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论他要我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever he told me to do to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.27,0:45:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论他想对我做什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Whatever he felt like doing to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.66,0:45:45.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要我亲哪里我都亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I kissed him where he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.20,0:45:46.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要我舔哪里我都舔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I licked him where he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:46.80,0:45:49.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要插进哪里我都配合\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I let him put himself where he wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:50.32,0:45:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是他的财物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I was his property.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.10,0:45:54.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会在他房间等上好几个小时\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I would wait in his chambers for hours
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.08,0:45:55.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,方便他无聊时拿我取乐\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}so he could use me when he was bored.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.14,0:45:59.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他还命我称他为"我的雄狮"  我照做了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}He ordered me to call him "my lion," so I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:01.46,0:46:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我捧着他的脸说\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I took his face in my hands and said,
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.57,0:46:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,"我是你的  你是我的"\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}"I am yours and you are mine."
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.32,0:46:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪伊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Shae.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:15.79,0:46:16.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Please don't.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.74,0:46:21.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是个妓女\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am a whore.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:23.03,0:46:23.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,记得吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:46:26.57,0:46:28.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那都是在他娶珊莎之前\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}That was before he married Sansa.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.00,0:46:31.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结婚以后  他只想要她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}After that, all he wanted was her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.06,0:46:33.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但珊莎不让他上床\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}But she wouldn't let him into her bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.31,0:46:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以他答应为她杀死乔佛里国王\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So he promised to kill King Joffrey for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.83,0:46:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:50.06,0:46:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要招供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wish to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:53.64,0:46:56.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要  招供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wish... to confess.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.73,0:47:00.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要招供\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You wish to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:03.26,0:47:04.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我救过你们\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saved you.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.33,0:47:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我拯救过这座城\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I saved this city
Dialogue: 0,0:47:09.06,0:47:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你们分文不值的贱命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}and all your worthless lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.00,0:47:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真该让史坦尼斯把你们全部灭掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I should have let Stannis kill you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:16.94,0:47:17.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,提利昂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Tyrion.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:21.75,0:47:23.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要招供吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Do you wish to confess?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:27.60,0:47:29.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  父亲\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Yes, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:30.44,0:47:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm guilty.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.48,0:47:35.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有罪  您不就是想听这一句吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Guilty. Is that what you want to hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:35.61,0:47:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你承认自己毒害了国王吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You admit you poisoned the king?
Dialogue: 0,0:47:37.46,0:47:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  这件事我是清白的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}No, of that I'm innocent.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:40.71,0:47:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我犯的是更可怕的罪\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I'm guilty of a far more monstrous crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.58,0:47:47.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的罪就是生为侏儒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I am guilty of being a dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:48.88,0:47:51.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不是一场对侏儒的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}You are not on trial for being a dwarf.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.32,0:47:53.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噢  就是\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Oh, yes, I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.97,0:47:57.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的一生就是一场对侏儒的审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I've been on trial for that my entire life.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:58.83,0:48:00.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有为自己辩护的吗\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Have you nothing to say in your defense?
Dialogue: 0,0:48:00.70,0:48:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有  只有一句\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Nothing but this--
Dialogue: 0,0:48:02.95,0:48:04.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没干过\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did not do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:05.42,0:48:07.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我没有杀乔佛里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I did not kill Joffrey,
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.95,0:48:10.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但我希望是我干的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}but I wish that I had.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:10.58,0:48:13.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着你那恶毒的小混蛋死掉\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Watching your vicious bastard die
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.21,0:48:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比干一千个撒谎的妓女还要痛快\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}gave me more relief than 1,000 lying whores.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.77,0:48:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我就是你们想象中的怪物\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wish I was the monster you think I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:26.09,0:48:29.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真希望我有足量的毒药毒死你们所有人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I wish I had enough poison for the whole pack of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.89,0:48:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看着你们吞进肚里  死了我也乐意\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I would gladly give my life to watch you all swallow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:34.64,0:48:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,马林爵士  马林爵士\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Ser Meryn. Ser Meryn.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.38,0:48:38.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带犯人回牢房\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}Escort the prisoner back to his cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.72,0:48:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不因为谋杀乔佛里而送命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I will not give my life for Joffrey's murder.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:45.28,0:48:47.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道在这儿得不到正义\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}And I know I'll get no justice here.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.12,0:48:51.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只能求助于天上诸神\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}So I will let the gods decide my fate.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:53.17,0:48:56.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要求比武审判\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}I demand a trial by combat.
